<h1 class="mar-b-xs">Switch</h1>
<h2 class="txt-gray-4 mar-t-none">A control for toggling binary values like on/off</h2>
<h2 id="demo">Demo</h2>
<code-sample>
  <input type="checkbox" is="switch" checked>
</code-sample>
<p>See more <a href="/examples#switch">examples</a></p>
